version_description: We've made some general improvements & bug fixes.

Hey there to all those making beautiful Quickart!
We’re excited to bring you some more options and give you even more art to explore. Here’s what’s new in this release:
- Urban Portrait is waiting to give your selfie an urban, graffiti feel
- Glitch Portrait just may make you feel like a modern Picasso
Have more ideas that you’d love to see? Let us know!
Yours,
The Quickart Team
We've made some general improvements & bug fixes.

Hey there!
Get excited for this new update! We're bringing you the following:
- Animal Kingdom: Bring out your inner animal
- Crop: Crop your creations for the optimal result
- Wrap Around: Twist it up with brand new spirals
Have an idea for a Quickart? Share it with us!
Yours,
The Quickart team

Hey there!
We've got a big update for you. We partnered with Sara Shakeel to create three amazing Artleaps:
- Diamond Sky: Light up the sky like a crystal dream
- Crystal Wonderland: Bring light and sparkle into your world
- Sparkling Art: Add unique sparkles to your face and body!
As always, if you have an idea for an Artleap feel free to share it with us. You might get it featured!
Yours,
The Artleap team

Hey Artleapers,
Can you feel it? The holidays are upon us! And with that some brand new features such as:
- Christmas Wonderland: Get the Christmas look you love
- Spread some Christmas cheer – new content out now!
Now share your art and make the holidays that much happier! And if you have any requests or ideas you'd like us to hear about then let us know at artleap.support@lightricks.com
Cheers,
The Artleap Team
